review: We did the Runaway train with Mac as our game master. He did a great job keeping the entire experience entertaining. It is one of the best rooms they have.

room_title: Escape room "Runaway Train" by Breakout Games - Dayton in Dayton
review: Great time with the whole family. The room was decorated so you had the feeling you were on a runaway train. Mac was fabulous as a game master giving us hints where needed (even singing a couple :) ). He made the experience a great time!
